0Thriller%20%E2%80%98A%20Place%20Called%20Silence%E2%80%99%20Makes%20%2450%20Million%20Debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720409657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fa-place-called-silence-3x2cr.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236062089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CA%20Place%20Called%20Silence%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Malaysian%20crime%20thriller%20that%20debuted%20at%20the%20Busan%20film%20festival%20in%202022%2C%20kicked%20off%20its%20commercial%20career%20in%20mainland%20China%20with%20a%20%2450%20million%20theatrical%20debut.%20The%20film%20earned%20RMB290%20million%20(%2440.9%20million)%20between%20Friday%20and%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20consultancy%20firm%20Artisan%20Gateway.%20It%20was%20given%20an%20early%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Patrick%20Frater%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fchina-box-office-crime-thriller-place-called-silence-big-debut-1236062089%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fchina-box-office-crime-thriller-place-called-silence-big-debut-1236062089%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fchina-box-office-crime-thriller-place-called-silence-big-debut-1236062089%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindenburg%20Profited%20By%20Sharing%20Adani%20Report%20With%20Client%20In%20Advance%3A%20SEBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20whose%20report%20critical%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20led%20to%20a%20massive%20stock%20rout%20last%20year%2C%20had%20shared%20an%20advanced%20copy%20with%20a%20client%20two%20months%20before%20publishing%20it%2C%20said%20the%20Indian%20markets%20regulator.%20This%20%26quot%3Bcollusion%26quot%3B%20led%20to%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20profits%20from%20a%20deal%20to%20share%20spoils%20from%20stock%20price%20movements%2C%20the%20Security%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20said%20in%20a%2046-page%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20Hindenburg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20details%20how%20New%20York-based%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20Mark%20Kingdon%20and%20a%20broker%20tied%20to%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20profited%20from%20the%20%24150%20billion%20rout%20in%20the%20market%20value%20of%2010%20listed%20firms%20of%20Adani%20Group%20after%20the%20report%20was%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20used%20%26quot%3Bnon-public%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20information%20to%20induce%20%26quot%3Bpanic%20selling%26quot%3B%20in%20Adani%20Group%20stocks%2C%20SEBI%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Hindenburg%20described%20the%20show-cause%20notice%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bsilence%20and%20intimidate%20those%20who%20expose%20corruption%20and%20fraud%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20most%20powerful%20individuals%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20the%20vehicle%20used%20to%20bet%20against%20Adani%20Enterprises%20belonged%20to%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20(International)%20Ltd%20(KMIL)%2C%20a%20Mauritius-based%20subsidiary%20of%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20Ltd.%20A%20fund%20of%20this%20subsidiary%20placed%20bets%20on%20Adani%20Enterprises%20for%20its%20client%2C%20Kingdon's%20Kingdon%20Capital%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Hindenburg%2C%20SEBI%20has%20issued%20notices%20to%20KMIL%2C%20Kingdon%20and%20Hindenburg%20founder%20Nathan%20Anderson%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime-stamped%20chats%20between%20a%20Kingdon%20employee%20and%20KMIL%20traders%20for%20selling%20future%20contracts%20in%20Adani%20Enterprises%20are%20part%20of%20the%20show-cause%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20said%20Kingdon%20neither%20disclosed%20their%20relationship%20with%20Hindenburg%20nor%20%26quot%3Bthat%20they%20were%20acting%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20any%20price-sensitive%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20SEBI%20had%20earlier%20given%20clean%20chits%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20lawyer%20Mahesh%20Jethmalani%20had%20earlier%20claimed%20that%20Kingdon%20had%20a%20Chinese%20link%20-%20the%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20is%20married%20a%20%26quot%3BChinese%20spy%26quot%3B%20Anla%20Cheng%2C%20he%20claimed.%20He%20alleged%20that%20the%20couple%20hired%20Hindenburg%20for%20the%20research%20report%20on%20Adani%20and%20engaged%20Kotak's%20services%20to%20make%20a%20trading%20account%20to%20short-sell%20Adani%20shares%2C%20and%20made%20millions%20from%20the%20stock%20rout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20further%20alleged%20Kingdon%20had%20a%20deal%20to%20share%20with%20Hindenburg%2030%25%20of%20the%20profits%20made%20from%20trading%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20report.%20It%20was%2C%20however%2C%20reduced%20to%2025%25%20due%20to%20the%20extra%20time%20and%20effort%20needed%20to%20reroute%20the%20trades%20via%20KMIL's%20K-India%20Opportunities%20Fund%20Ltd%20fund.%20Kingdon%20had%20a%20controlling%20stake%20in%20the%20K-India%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKingdon%20transferred%20%2443%20million%20in%20two%20phases%20to%20build%20short%20positions%20for%208.5%20lakh%20shares%20of%20Adani%20Enterprises%20before%20the%20report%20against%20Adani%20Group%20was%20published.%20Hindenburg%20published%20it%20during%20the%20pre-market%20hours%20on%20January%2024%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrior%20to%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20Report%2C%20concentration%20in%20short-selling%20activity%20was%20observed%20in%20the%20derivatives%20of%20Adani%20Enterprises%20Ltd%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SEBI%20said.%20After%20the%20report%20was%20published%2C%20the%20Adani%20Enterprises%20share%20prices%20fell%20by%20around%2059%25%20between%20January%2024%20and%20February%2022%2C%202023%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20K-India%20fund%2C%20which%20had%20opened%20a%20trading%20account%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20report's%20publication%2C%20squared%20off%20its%20entire%20short%20position%20and%20made%20profits%20of%20around%20%2422.25%20million%20(Rs%20183.23%20crore).%20%26quot%3BThe%20net%20profit%20after%20trading%20and%20legal%20expenses%20comes%20to%20USD%2022.11%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20SEBI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKingdon%2C%20who%20owed%20%245.5%20million%20to%20Hindenburg%20as%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20paid%20%244.1%20million%20by%20June%201%2C%20the%20notice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20notice%2C%20Kingdon%20Capital%20said%20it%20had%20legal%20option%20to%20%26quot%3Benter%20into%20a%20research%20services%20agreement%20with%20a%20third-party%20firm%20that%20publicly%20releases%20short%20reports%20on%20companies%2C%20pursuant%20to%20which%20Kingdon%20Capital%20would%20be%20given%20a%20draft%20copy%20of%20the%20report%20before%20it%20is%20made%20publicly%20available%20and%20would%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20accordingly%20made%20investments%20before%20the%20report's%20public%20dissemination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20said%20it%20had%20made%20%244.1%20million%20from%20its%20declared%20positions%20on%20Adani%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720409580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ffhsjisso_sebi_625x300_02_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fhindenburg-profited-by-sharing-adani-report-with-client-in-advance-sebi-6057248%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20whose%20report%20critical%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20led%20to%20a%20massive%20stock%20rout%20last%20year%2C%20had%20shared%20an%20advanced%2