s%20him%20a%20sense%20of%20satisfaction%20and%20doesn't%20take%20any%20stress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fi-want-to-be-part-of-all-three-formats-ishan-kishan-aims-for-a-comeback-to-the-indian-cricket-team%2Farticleshow%2F111565257.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Ishan%20Rejected%20BCCI%20Order%20To%20Play%20Ranji%20Trophy%3F%20Real%20Reason%20Revealed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20wicketkeeper%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20opened%20up%20on%20him%20taking%20a%20break%20from%20international%20cricket%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20ouster%20from%20the%20team.%20Kishan%20last%20played%20for%20India%20during%20the%20third%20T20I%20of%20a%20five-match%20series%20against%20Australia%20in%20November%20last%20year.%20He%20was%20then%20named%20in%20the%20subsequent%20tour%20of%20South%20Africa%2C%20but%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20Test%20series%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons.%20After%20taking%20a%20short%20break%2C%20Kishan%20also%20decided%20to%20skip%20Ranji%20Trophy%20matches%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20BCCI%20removing%20him%20from%20the%20central%20contracts%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Dravid%2C%20who%20was%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20India%20at%20that%20time%2C%20has%20suggested%20that%20if%20Kishan%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%2C%20he%20must%20feature%20and%20perform%20in%20domestic%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20decision%20to%20skip%20domestic%20matches%20led%20to%20severe%20criticism%2C%20Kishan%20has%20now%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20not%20in%20the%20right%20frame%20of%20mind%20to%20play%20Ranji%20Trophy%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20a%20break%20and%20I%20think%20it%20was%20normal.%20There%20is%20a%20rule%20that%20if%20you%20want%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20you%20must%20perform%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%20It%20is%20as%20simple%20as%20that.%20Now%2C%20it%20was%20very%20different%20for%20me%20to%20play%20domestic%20cricket%20as%20it%20was%20not%20making%20any%20sense.%20I%20was%20not%20in%20a%20frame%20of%20mind%20to%20play%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20took%20a%20break%20from%20international%20cricket.%20It%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20that%20you%20take%20a%20break%20from%20international%20cricket%20and%20then%20you%20go%20and%20play%20domestic%20matches.%20Fir%20toh%20aap%20international%20hi%20khelte%20(Then%20I%20could%20have%20continued%20playing%20for%20India)%2C%26quot%3B%20Kishan%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fishan-kishan-on-his-time-away-from-team-india-i-took-a-break-as-i-wasnt-feeling-right-no-one-understood-my-situation-9438037%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20also%20admitted%20that%20he%20was%20disappointed%20with%20him%20not%20getting%20enough%20playing%20time%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20despite%20performing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20depressing.%20Today%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20that%20everything%20was%20fine.%20It%20was%20not%20easy%20for%20me%20at%20all.%20You%20go%20through%20a%20lot.%20Mere%20dimag%20mey%20ye%20sab%20chalta%20raha%20ki%20yaar%20kya%20hoga%20gaya%2C%20kyu%20ho%20gaya%2C%20mere%20saath%20kyu%20(Questions%20like%20what%20happened%2C%20why%20me).%20All%20these%20things%20happened%20when%20I%20was%20performing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20skipping%20the%20South%20Africa%20tour%20and%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20Kishan%20returned%20to%20action%20during%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20scored%20just%20320%20runs%20from%2014%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2022.85%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20148.83.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20he%20was%20not%20considered%20for%20T20%20World%20Cup%20selection%2C%20with%20the%20management%20picking%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanju%20Samson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1701-sanju-samson-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanju%20Samson%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20two%20wicketkeepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720407840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fla1h6ujo_ishan-kishan-afp_625x300_12_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fishan-kishan-reveals-reason-behind-ranji-trophy-snub-despite-bcci-mandate-6053381%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ishan%20Kishan%20has%20opened%20up%20on%20him%20taking%20a%20break%20from%20international%20cricket%2C%20and%20skipping%20domestic%20matches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fishan-kishan-reveals-reason-behind-ranji-trophy-snub-despite-bcci-mandate-6053381%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fishan-kishan-reveals-reason-behind-ranji-trophy-snub-despite-bcci-mandate-6053381%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fishan-kishan-reveals-reason-behind-ranji-trophy-snub-despite-bcci-mandate-6053381%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20B%20performs%20'shiva%20abhishek'%20at%20his%20home%20temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720407605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111565086%2Cimgsize-113944.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famitabh-bachchan-perfo