h%20that%20those%20who%20created%20the%20chaos%20will%20not%20be%20spared.%20Through%20my%20lawyer%20AP%20Singh%2C%20I%20have%20requested%20the%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20to%20stand%20with%20the%20bereaved%20families%20and%20the%20injured%20and%20help%20them%20throughout%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20'Baba'%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stampede%20occurred%20during%20the%20'Satsang'%20of%20self-styled%20godman%20Suraj%20Pal%20Singh%2C%20known%20as%20'Bhole%20Baba'%2C%20in%20Fulari%20village%2C%20Hathras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720407120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F63irg0r8_ap-singh-lawyer_625x300_08_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoison-sprayed-at-hathras-event-led-to-stampede-claims-godmans-lawyer-6055897%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20121%20people%20were%20killed%20due%20to%20a%20stampede%20at%20a%20religious%20gathering%20in%20Hathras%2C%20advocate%20AP%20Singh%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20incident%20that%20took%20the%20lives%20of%20121%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%20occurred%20because%20unidentified%20men%20sprayed%20poison.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoison-sprayed-at-hathras-event-led-to-stampede-claims-godmans-lawyer-6055897%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoison-sprayed-at-hathras-event-led-to-stampede-claims-godmans-lawyer-6055897%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoison-sprayed-at-hathras-event-led-to-stampede-claims-godmans-lawyer-6055897%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Leonardo%2C%20Kate%20mourn%20'Titanic'%20producer's%2