back%20and%20in%20their%20cribs%2C%20husbands%20kill%20their%20wives%20to%20secure%20more%20advantageous%20marriages%2C%20and%20women%20tragically%20die%20in%20childbirth.%20Rhaenyra%20and%20Aegon%20II%20Targaryen's%20war%20over%20the%20Iron%20Throne%20isn't%20pretty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20ranked%20the%2010%20saddest%20deaths%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20seasons%20one%20and%20two%20below%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E10.%20Viserys%20died%20after%20a%20long%20bout%20of%20illness.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20his%2050s%20with%20long%20silver%20hair%20and%20wearing%20a%20gold%20crown%20looks%20pensively%20out%20towards%20a%20crowd.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885bb31aace5b3ada4d351%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaddy%20Considine%20as%20King%20Viserys%20Targaryen%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHear%20us%20out%3A%20We%20loved%20Paddy%20Considine%20as%20Viserys%2C%20but%20his%20death%20was%20so%20written%20on%20the%20wall%20that%20it%20couldn't%20even%20bring%20much%20surprise%20or%20sadness.%20For%20one%2C%20it's%20necessary%20to%20kick%20off%20a%20war%20of%20succession.%20But%20more%20importantly%2C%20it%20was%20preceded%20by%20a%20long%2C%20leprosy-like%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20first%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%2C%26quot%3B%20Viserys'%20health%20gradually%20declines%20as%20his%20children%20grow%20older%20and%20the%20issue%20of%20his%20succession%20grows%20more%20salient.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20his%20life%2C%20his%20illness%20has%20progressed%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20you're%20kind%20of%20hoping%20the%20guy%20will%20die.%20Too%20bad%20his%20final%20words%20brought%20about%20such%20a%20huge%20misunderstanding%20that%20it%20launched%20an%20entire%20Targaryen%20family%20civil%20war.%20Whoops!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20we%20mourn%20Viserys%20and%20the%20comparative%20peace%20of%20his%20era%20%E2%80%94%20but%20without%20his%20death%2C%20we%20really%20wouldn't%20have%20a%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E9.%20Daemon%20murders%20his%20first%20wife%2C%20Lady%20Rhea%20Royce.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rachel%20redford%20as%20lady%20rhea%20royce%20in%20house%20of%20the%20dragon%2C%20a%20young%20woman%20with%20brown%20hair%20pulled%20half%20back%2C%20wearing%20brown%20armor%20and%20sitting%20astride%20a%20white%20horse%2C%20riding%20through%20a%20grassland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668860881f0c1cd6d731f69a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20Redford%20as%20Lady%20Rhea%20in%20season%20one%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20barely%20got%20to%20know%20Lady%20Rhea%20in%20season%20one%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20most%20of%20what%20we%20knew%20of%20her%20came%20from%20Daemon's%20mouth.%20Given%20that%20he%20referred%20to%20her%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BBronze%20Bitch%26quot%3B%20and%20refused%20to%20consummate%20their%20marriage%2C%20most%20of%20those%20words%20weren't%20very%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20meet%20her%20briefly%20in%20season%20one%2C%20episode%20five%2C%20shortly%20before%20Daemon%2C%20well%E2%80%A6%20murders%20her.%20Rhea%20seems%20independent%2C%20capable%2C%20and%20unafraid%20to%20taunt%20Daemon.%20That%20is%20until%20she%20clearly%20realizes%20that%20he's%20come%20to%20kill%20her%20and%20attempt%20to%20marry%20Rhaenrya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Rhea's%20death%20comes%20off%20more%20as%20a%20shock%2C%20given%20her%20little%20screentime%2C%20it's%20tragic%20to%20see%20her%20merely%20as%20a%20casualty%20of%20Daemon's%20ambition%20and%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E8.%20Lyonel%20and%20Harwin%20Strong%20die%20at%20Harrenhal%2C%20in%20a%20plot%20orchestrated%20by%20Larys%20Strong.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22left%3A%20ser%20harwin%20strong%2C%20a%20young%20man%20with%20chin%20length%20curly%20brown%20hair%20and%20facial%20hair.%20he's%20looking%20kindly%20to%20the%20side%2C%20and%20wearing%20armor%3B%20right%3A%20lyonel%20strong%2C%20a%20middle%20aged%20man%20with%20a%20receding%20hairline%2C%20facial%20hair%2C%20and%20black%20robes%2C%20looking%20stern%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6688600d1aace5b3ada4d444%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarwin%20and%20Lyonel%20Strong%20both%20died%20at%20the%20command%20of%20Larys%20Strong%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESer%20Harwin%20Strong%20and%20his%20father%20Lyonel%2C%20for%20some%20time%20the%20Hand%20of%20the%20King%2C%20weren't%20particularly%20beloved%20characters.%20But%20their%20tragic%20death%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20one%20of%20their%20own%20%E2%80%94%20Larys%20Strong%20%E2%80%94%20was%20still%20rather%20striking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20birth%20of%20Rhaenyra's%20third%20son%2C%20Joffrey%2C%20Harwin%20got%20into%20an%20altercation%20with%20Ser%20Criston%20Cole%20after%20Criston%20insinuated%20that%20Harwin%20was%20Jacaerys%20and%20Lucerys'%20father.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20event%2C%20Lyonel%20attempted%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20position%20as%20Hand%2C%20citing%20the%20dishonor%20that%20Harwin%20brought%20on%20their%20family.%20Viserys%20rejects%20his%20resignation%20but%20allows%20him%20to%20escort%20Harwin%20back%20to%20Harrenhal.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Larys'%20plot%20is%20waiting%20for%20them%3A%20both%20men%20die%20in%20a%20fire%20once%20they%20make%20it%20back%20to%20the%20castle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarwin%2C%20despite%20clearly%20being%20hot-blooded%2C%20seems%20like%20an%20alright%20guy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20pretty%20cruel%20to%20kill%20him%20right%20after%20Jacaerys%20realizes%20that%20Harwin%20is%20his%20father.%20And%20compared%20to%20other%20Hands%20(i.e.%20Otto%20Hightower)%2C%20Lyonel%20seemed%20relatively%20unbiased%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20crown.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E7.%20Jahaerys%20Targaryen%20is%20murdered%20after%20a%20miscommunication.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olivia%20Cooke%2C%20Phia%20Saban%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20season%202%20episode%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885f6f1f0c1cd6d731f652%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlicent%20and%20Helaena%20attend%20the%20procession%20behind%20Jaehaerys'%20body.%3Cp%3ETheo%20Whitman%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeason%20two%20kicked%20things%20off%20by%20adapting%20an%20infamous%20murder%20from%20%26quot%3BFire%20and%20Blood%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Daemon%20sends%20two%20mercenaries%2C%20Blood%20(Sam%20C%20Wilson)%20and%20Cheese%20(Mark%20Stobbart)%20to%20murder%20Aemond%20in%20revenge%20for%20the%20death%20of%20Lucerys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20duo%20fails%20to%20find%20the%20prince%20in%20the%20Red%20Keep%2C%20they%20instead%20go%20to%20plan%20b%3A%20%26quot%3Ba%20son%20for%20a%20son.%26quot%3B%20They%20find%20Helaena%20Targaryen%20(Phia%20Saban)%20and%20force%20her%20to%20point%20out%20which%20sleeping%20toddler%20is%20her%20son.%20Although%20she%20briefly%20tries%20to%20fool%20Blood%20and%20Cheese%20by%20pointing%20at%20her%20daughter%2C%20they%20call%20her%20bluff%20and%20descend%20upon%20Jaeharys%20with%20knives%2C%20cutting%20his%20head%20off%20in%20his%20crib.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20the%20audience%20doesn't%20see%20the%20horror%20unfold%20because%20Helaena%20flees%20the%20room.%20But%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20brutality%20is%20displayed%20for%20all%20of%20King's%20Landing%20to%20see%20during%20Jaeharys'%20funeral%20procession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20conflict%20between%20the%20greens%20and%20the%20blacks%2C%20an%20innocent%20child%20was%20slaughtered%20because%20of%20the%20squabble%20over%20the%20throne%2C%20and%20it's%20clear%20to%20everyone%20that%20the%20conflict%20has%20been%20taken%20beyond%20the%20point%20of%20no%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E6.%20Arryk%20and%20Erryk%20Cargyll%20killed%20each%20other%20after%20ending%20up%20on%20different%20sides%20of%20the%20war.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22House%20of%20the%20Dragon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885ca31f0c1cd6d731f5bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EErryk%20(Ellliot%20Tittensor)%20and%20Arryk%20(Luke%20Tittensor)%20Cargylle%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20Arryk%20Cargyll%20and%20Erryk%20Cargyll%20had%20more%20control%20over%20their%20deaths%2C%20since%20they%20chose%20to%20fight%20till%20the%20end%2C%20that%20doesn't%20make%20their%20deaths%20any%20less%20sad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20season%20one%2C%20the%20twins%20work%20together%20as%20Kingsguard%20protecting%20the%20royal%20family.%20But%20when%20the%20Greens%20usurp%20the%20throne%2C%20they%20are%20split%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Arryk%20sides%20with%20Aegon%20II%20while%20Erryk%20leaves%20and%20joins%20Rhaenyra's%20Queensguard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Criston%20Cole%20sends%20Arryk%20to%20slay%20Rhaenyra%20in%20episode%20two%2C%20the%20brothers'%20impending%20showdown%20begins.%20The%20scene%20is%20a%20messy%2C%20vicious%20fight%2C%20and%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20tell%20which%20twin%20wins.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20slaying%20his%20brother%2C%20Erryk%20stabs%20themselves%20with%20their%20sword%20after%20realizing%20what%20he%20has%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20heartbreaking%20that%20these%20twins%20are%20forced%20to%20pick%20duty%20over%20their%20own%20kin.%20Their%20deaths%20highlight%20how%20painful%20and%20destructive%20this%20civil%20war%20will%20be%20for%20the%20non-royal%20members%20of%20Westeros.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E5.%20Joffrey%20Lonmouth%20was%20brutally%20beaten%20to%20death%20by%20Criston%20Cole.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20with%20shoulder-length%20hair%20stand%20side%20by%20side%20looking%20serious.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885f27268f62ba18a7e1f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoffrey%20and%20Criston%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJoffrey%20Lonmouth's%20death%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20we%20really%20saw%20Ser%20Criston%20Cole's%20true%20colors%2C%20and%20man%2C%20were%20they%20ugly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Rhaenyra%20and%20Laenor%20Velaryon%20were%20wed%2C%20they%20both%20had%20an%20understanding%20that%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20pursue%20their%20other%20lovers%3A%20Criston%20and%20Joffrey.%20At%20their%20wedding%2C%20Joffrey%20confronts%20Criston.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20know%20me%2C%20Ser%20Criston%2C%20but%20we%20are%20both%20deeply%20invested%20in%20this%20union%2C%26quot%3B%20Joffrey%20says.%20He%20tells%20Criston%20that%20Laenor%20is%20%26quot%3Bdear%26quot%3B%20to%20him%2C%20and%20that%20he%20understands%20Criston%20and%20Rhaenyra's%20relationship.%20It's%20a%20strategic%20move%20meant%20to%20unite%20them%20all%20in%20the%20shared%20secret%20of%20Laenor%20and%20Rhaenyra's%20marriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that's%20not%20what%20happens.%20Instead%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20revelry%2C%20Criston%20brutally%20slays%20Joffrey%2C%20striking%20Laenor%20in%20the%20process.%20While%20we%20didn't%20know%20him%20particularly%20well%2C%20Joffrey%20didn't%20do%20anything%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20certainly%20nothing%20to%20merit%20Criston%20beating%20his%20face%20into%20a%20bloody%2C%20lifeless%20pulp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suddenness%2C%20brutality%2C%20and%20abject%20loss%20on%20Laenor's%20part%20of%20Joffrey's%20death%20merit%20its%20place%20on%20this%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E4.%20Laena%20Velaryon%20ordered%20Vhagar%20to%20kill%20her%20by%20fire.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20with%20silvery%20curled%20hair%20and%20regal%20jewelry.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885d24268f62ba18a7e173%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELaena%20Velaryon%2C%20now%20married%20to%20Daemon%20Targaryen%2C%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20season%20features%20a%20second%20agonizing%20pregnancy-related%20death%2C%20as%20Laena%20Velaryon%20(Nanna%20Blondell)%20takes%20her%20own%20life%20in%20episode%20six.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20marrying%20Daemon%20and%20moving%20to%20Pentos%2C%20Laena%20struggles%20with%20a%20complicated%20birth%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20is%20offered%20the%20same%20choice%20that%20Viserys%20had%3A%20save%20his%20wife%2C%20or%20save%20the%20baby.%20However%2C%20Laena%20takes%20control%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20decides%20her%20own%20fate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20goes%20to%20her%20dragon%2C%20Vhagar%2C%20and%20commands%20him%20to%20burn%20her%20alive%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bdracarys%26quot%3B%20command.%20It's%20upsetting%20because%20Laena%20is%20forced%20into%20that%20situation%2C%20albeit%20at%20least%20it's%20her%20own%20decision.%20But%20seeing%20how%20reluctant%20Vhagar%20is%20to%20kill%20his%20rider%20just%20makes%20the%20whole%20scene%20even%20more%20upsetting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20Rhaenys%20sacrifices%20herself%20and%20her%20dragon%2C%20Meleys%2C%20at%20Rook's%20Rest.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22716%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22eve%20best%20and%20steve%20toussaint%20as%20rhaenys%20and%20corlys%20in%20house%20of%20the%20dragon%2C%20standing%20at%20the%20head%20of%20a%20council%20table.%20both%20are%20wearing%20black%20clothing%2C%20with%20their%20silver%20hair%20worn%20long%2C%20and%20rhaenys%20crosses%20her%20arms%20as%20she%20looks%20towards%20corlys%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885eb3268f62ba18a7e1d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22537%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEve%20Best%20and%20Steve%20Toussaint%20as%20Rhaenys%20and%20Corlys%20Velaryon%20in%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20Rhaenys%20headed%20off%20to%20Rook's%20Rest%2C%20there%20was%20already%20a%20sense%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20make%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20three%2C%20she%20conversed%20with%20her%20husband%20about%20their%20legacy.%20Criston%20Cole%20and%20Aemond%20Targaryen%20clearly%20had%20a%20secret%20plan%20up%20their%20sleeves.%20There%20were%20too%20many%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20make%20her%20death%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Aemond%20and%20Vhagar%20any%20less%20tragic.%20Across%20the%20two%20seasons%2C%20Rhaenys%20has%20been%20brave%2C%20virtuous%2C%20loyal%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20badass%2C%20making%20her%20a%20favorite%20among%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20she%20realizes%20that%20she%20cannot%20defeat%20Vhagar%20at%20the%20battle%20of%20Rook's%20Rest%20in%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20four%2C%20she%20doesn't%20run%20away.%20Instead%2C%20she%20straps%20herself%20tighter%20in%20her%20seat%20and%20fights%20valiantly%20till%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20true%20noble%20warriors%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20is%20now%20gone%2C%20and%20to%20quote%20Otto%20Hightower%2C%20We%20(the%20audience%20and%20Westeros)%20%26quot%3Bare%20poorer%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20Queen%20Aemma%20dies%20during%20childbirth%20after%20Viserys%20orders%20his%20son%20to%20be%20cut%20out%20of%20her.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20woman%20with%20silver%20hair%20wearing%20medieval%20royalty%20garb%20stand%20lovingly%20next%20to%20each%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885ee21f0c1cd6d731f633%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaddy%20Considine%20and%20Sian%20Brooke%20costar%20as%20King%20Viserys%20and%20Queen%20Aemma%20in%20HBO's%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20made%20a%20bloody%20debut%20in%20the%20premiere%20episode%20of%20the%20first%20season%20with%20the%20heartbreaking%20death%20of%20King%20Viserys'%20(Paddy%20Considine)%20wife%2C%20Queen%20Aemma%20(Sian%20Brooke).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aemma%20goes%20into%20labor%2C%20the%20baby%20gets%20stuck%2C%20and%20Viserys%20is%20forced%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20save%20his%20wife%20or%20the%20baby.%20The%20King%20chooses%20his%20unborn%20child%20hoping%20to%20get%20a%20male%20heir%20to%20the%20Targaryen%20throne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20maesters%20cut%20Aemma's%20belly%20open%20to%20save%20the%20child%2C%20killing%20her%20in%20the%20process.%20It's%20tragic%20because%20Aemma's%20agency%20is%20taken%20away%20from%20her%2C%20and%20she's%20completely%20disregarded%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20male%20heir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20devastating%20scene%20is%20only%20made%20worse%20when%20the%20baby%2C%20Baelon%2C%20dies%20just%20one%20day%20after%20being%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20Lucerys%20is%20the%20first%20major%20casualty%20of%20the%20Dance%20of%20the%20Dragons.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rhaenyra%2C%20emma%20d'arcy%2C%20holding%20her%20sun%20lucerys%2C%20elliot%20grihault%2C%20in%20front%20of%20a%20strategy%20war%20table.%20she's%20looking%20at%20him%20intensely%2C%20and%20cracling%20his%20neck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66885f0b1aace5b3ada4d411%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElliot%20Grihault%20and%20Emma%20D'Arcy%20as%20Lucerys%20and%20Rhaenyra%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELucerys%20and%20his%20dragon%20Arrax's%20deaths%20are%20truly%20the%20biggest%20tragedies%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Greens%20and%20the%20Blacks%20were%20preparing%20for%20an%20eventual%20war%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20they%20could%20have%20found%20another%20way%20to%20settle%20the%20throne%20debate%20after%20a%20cooling-off%20period.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20reconciliation%20once%20Lucerys%2C%20a%20child%20and%20an%20heir%2C%20is%20slain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20Lucerys'%20death%20essentially%20kick-start%20a%20terrible%20civil%20war%2C%20but%20it%20was%20entirely%20accidental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20scene%20itself%20is%20almost%20like%20a%20horror%20movie%2C%20with%20Aemond%20and%20Vhagar%20stalking%20and%20taunting%20Lucerys%20and%20Arrax%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20rainy%20skies.%20Aemond%20sees%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20toy%20with%20and%20harm%20Lucerys%20as%20revenge%20for%20his%20eye%2C%2