can't%20continue.%20There's%20no%20living%20after%20that.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20a%20sacrificial%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238bc03b3-dbcd-453f-b619-1dff1827163e%5C%22%3ERhaenys%20still%20exercises%20restraint%20during%20her%20final%20battle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERhaenys'%20actual%20death%20comes%20during%20a%20three-way%20dragon%20fight%20between%20Meleys%2C%20Vhagar%2C%20and%20Sunfyre.%20The%20emotional%20impact%20of%20that%20battle%20hinges%20on%20Best's%20performance.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-of-the-dragon-rhaenyra-lucerys-death-scene-director-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDirector%20Alan%20Taylor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20also%20directed%20the%20series%20premiere%2C%20doesn't%20hesitate%20to%20cut%20in%20close%20to%20her%20face%20as%20it%20becomes%20increasingly%20streaked%20with%20ash.%20Best%20effectively%20communicates%20Rhaenys'%20resolve%20%E2%80%94%20and%20her%20resignation%20to%20death%20%E2%80%94%20over%20the%20course%20of%20several%20stark%20close-up%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20it%20more%20remarkable%20are%20the%20conditions%20under%20which%20Best%20acted%20out%20Rhaenys'%20last%20moments.%20It%20took%20Best%20two%20weeks%20to%20film%20the%20sequence%2C%20working%20alone%20while%20on%20a%20mechanized%20mount.%20Rhaenys'%20final%20moments%20were%20filmed%20amid%20the%20chaos%20of%20wind%20blowing%20in%20Best's%20face%20and%20shouted%20directions%20as%20she%20mimicked%20difficult%20maneuvers%20on%20dragonback%20while%20%26quot%3Bclinging%20on%20for%20dear%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20having%20to%20do%20the%20whole%20story%20in%20your%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20Best%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20just%20the%20battle%2C%20and%20seeing%20everybody%20and%20responding%20to%20the%20physical%20nature%20of%20the%20battle%2C%20but%20also%20obviously%20the%20emotional%20part%20of%20what's%20going%20on%20inside%2C%20which%20is%20challenging%20in%20the%20contex