t-global-agrees-to-merge-with-skydance-shari-redstone-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Mihir%20Shah%3F%20Shiv%20Sena%20Leader's%20Son%20Accused%20In%20Mumbai%20BMW%20Hit-And-Run%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20speeding%20BMW%2C%20allegedly%20driven%20by%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader's%20son%2C%20hit%20a%20two-wheeler%20in%20Mumbai's%20Worli%20on%20Sunday%20killing%20a%2045-year-old%20woman%20and%20injuring%20her%20husband.%20Fish%20sellers%20Kaveri%20and%20Pradip%20Nakhva%20were%20returning%20after%20buying%20fish%20from%20Sassoon%20Dock%20when%20their%20scooter%20was%20hit%20from%20behind%20by%20the%20car.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20were%20flung%20in%20the%20air%20and%20landed%20on%20the%20car's%20bonnet.%20While%20Pradeep%20managed%20to%20jump%20off%20it%2C%20Kaveri%20was%20dragged%20for%20100%20metres.%20She%20died%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%2C%2024-year-old%20Mihir%20Shah%2C%20who%20was%20driving%20the%20car%20while%20drunk%20has%20been%20on%20the%20run%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWho%20is%20Mihir%20Shah%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shah%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Rajesh%20Shah%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Palghar%20district.%20The%20politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir%20studied%20till%20Class%2010%20and%20did%20not%20pursue%20any%20further%20education.%20He%20joined%20his%20father's%20construction%20business%20based%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%20the%20accident%2C%20Mihir%20was%20out%20till%20late%20at%20night%20drinking%20in%20Juhu.%20In%20a%20drunk%20state%2C%20he%20asked%20his%20driver%20Rajendra%20Singh%20Bijawat%20to%20take%20him%20on%20a%20long%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20driving%20from%20Juhu%20to%20Worli%2C%20he%20told%20the%20driver%20he%20would%20take%20the%20wheel%20and%20drive%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20way.%20The%20accident%20happened%20