Mays'%202013%20resume%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Mays%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20eight-year%20stint%20at%20Google%2C%20Mays%20left%20the%20company%20to%20start%20his%20own%20tech%20career%20consultancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20his%202013%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-engineer-meta-sap-salesforce-tesla-amazon-linkedin-jobs-branding-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Er%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20career%20coach%20said%20there%20were%20three%20things%20he%20likes%20and%20three%20things%20he%20would%20change%20if%20he%20were%20to%20re-write%20the%20document%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f41c675b-bfdc-4cf1-ac5c-5dc696837d96%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20what%20he%20would%20keep%20the%20same%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeparate%20skills%20section%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20that%20I%20thought%20was%20super%20useful%20was%20having%20those%20skills%20and%20languages%20along%20the%20right%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20the%20second%20column%20of%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20there's%20a%20lot%20more%20stuff%20that%20I%20know%20just%20because%20it%20takes%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20vertical%20real%20estate.%26quot%3B%20This%20layout%20also%20helped%20people%20quickly%20get%20to%20the%20experience%20section.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20before%20the%20how%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMays%20liked%20that%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20emphasized%20the%20impact%20he%20created.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can%20convince%20somebody%20that%20what%20I%20did%20was%20important%2C%20then%20they'll%20want%20to%20know%20how%20I%20did%20it.%26quot%3B%20For%20example%2C%20he%20added%20that%20his%20enhancements%20increased%20the%20speed%20of%20deployment%20by%2050%25.%20Then%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20tell%20you%20how%20I%20did%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20did%20that%20by%20using%20zip%20compression%20tools%20and%20algorithms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimplify%20jargon%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20technical%20jargon%20like%20names%20of%20software%2C%20Mays%20was%20careful%20not%20to%20assume%20that%20everyone%20reading%20his%20resume%20would%20know%20what%20some%20abbreviations%20mean.%20Just%20like%20formal%20writing%2C%20he%20uses%20the%20full%20names%20for%20each%20of%20those%20software%20on%20first%20mention%2C%20and%20use%20short%20forms%20after%20that.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20know%20your%20industry%20to%20know%20when%20it%20is%20appropriate%20to%20rely%20on%20an%20abbreviation%20versus%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5d2a4cc-f88a-4e9b-8e2f-de5b3259ee8f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20changes%20he%20would%20make%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20numbers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20To%20better%20show%20impact%2C%20Mays%20would%20include%20more%20datapoints%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20work.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20a%20project%20to%20support%20a%20system%20for%20an%20e-commerce%20platform.%20For%20a%20big%20sales%20day%20like%20Black%20Friday%2C%20he%20would%20have%20highlighted%20how%20many%20thousands%20of%20people%20used%20the%20website%20per%20second%20to%20show%20the%20scale%20he%20was%20working%20at.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EProfessional%20summary%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mays%20said%20that%20his%202013%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20also%20lacked%20a%20professional%20summary.%20%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20is%20going%20to%20tell%20a%20story%2C%20and%20it's%20your%20job%20as%20the%20storyteller%20to%20make%20that%20narrative%20as%20easy%20to%20understand%20for%20someone%20who's%20only%20going%20to%20look%20at%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20for%20maybe%20five%20seconds.%26quot%3B%20The%20summary%20should%20say%20why%20you're%20the%20perfect%20person%20for%20the%20role%2C%20he%20said.%20In%20his%20latest%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20Mays%20added%20three%20lines%20summarizing%20h