ed%20even%20if%20the%20LFI's%20firebrand%20figurehead%20Jean-Luc%20Melenchon%20is%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Minister%20Stephane%20Sejourne%2C%20who%20leads%20Macron's%20party%2C%20ruled%20out%20that%20Melenchon%20%26quot%3Band%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20his%20allies%26quot%3B%20would%20govern%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Laurent%20Wauquiez%2C%20a%20senior%20figure%20among%20traditional%20right-wing%20lawmakers%2C%20who%20won%20his%20seat%2C%20appeared%20to%20rule%20out%20entering%20into%20any%20coalition%20with%20Macron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Tide%20is%20rising'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron's%20own%20popularity%20has%20hit%20such%20a%20low%20that%20he%20stayed%20totally%20out%20of%20the%20final%20week%20of%20the%20election%20campaign%2C%20not%20making%20a%20single%20comment%20in%20public%20as%20the%20vastly%20more%20popular%20Attal%20took%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20voting%20Sunday%20he%20mingled%20with%20well-wishers%20in%20Le%20Touquet%2C%20but%20did%20not%20repeat%20his%20walk%20through%20the%20fashionable%20Channel%20resort%20in%20a%20bomber%20jacket%20and%20baseball%20cap%20as%20he%20did%20in%20the%20June%2030%20first%20round%2C%20seen%20as%20arrogant%20by%20some%20supporters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20manoeuvring%20will%20intensify%20beneath%20him.%20Interior%20Minister%20Gerald%20Darmanin%2C%20who%20won%20his%20seat%2C%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20he%20plans%20to%20be%20a%20leading%20voice%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%2C%20possibly%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20faction%20of%20Philippe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20far%20right%20was%20defeated%20in%20these%20elections%2C%20its%20three-time%20presidential%20candidate%20Marine%20Le%20Pen%20said%20she%20believed%20this%20would%20have%20no%20impact%20on%20her%20ambition%20to%20win%20the%20Elysee%20Palace%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tide%20is%20rising.%20It%20did%20not%20rise%20