ning%20at%20the%20Central%20Institute%20for%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20nucleating%20mussels%2C%20we%20put%20them%20in%20small%20nets%20and%20transferred%20them%20into%20the%20pond.%20This%20process%20took%20us%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half.%20But%20the%20work%20was%20not%20yet%20finished.%20We%20had%20to%20maintain%20the%20pond%20thereafter.%20Every%20month%2C%20we%20added%20feed%20and%20maintained%20oxygen%20in%20the%20pond%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20mussels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2021%20months%20of%20patiently%20waiting%20for%20the%20mussels%20to%20turn%20into%20pearls%2C%20Gaurav%20finally%20got%20the%20results.%20%E2%80%9COur%20happiness%20knew%20no%20bounds.%20We%20fetched%20Rs%20110%20per%20pearl%20and%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%201.25%20crore%20and%20made%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2080%20lakh.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20this%20profit%20in%20a%201.5%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20land%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20us.%20Farmers%20in%20200%20villages%20collectively%20could%20not%20earn%20this%20much%20by%20growing%20wheat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20I%20earned%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20after%20investing%20Rs%2021%20lakh.%20This%20was%202.5%20times%20earnings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20beams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20feat%20was%20not%20as%20easy.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20challenges%20in%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20is%20managing%20weather%20conditions.%20Rajasthan%20has%20very%20warm%20weather%20and%20it%20took%20two%20days%20of%20travel%20by%20train%20to%20source%20mussels%20from%20Odisha.%20In%20this%20process%2C%20the%20mussels%20became%20very%20weak%20as%20they%20were%20without%20water%20for%20so%20long%2C%20which%20increased%20the%20mortality%20rate%20to%2050%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20pearl%20farming%20in%20the%20extreme%2